      Part4: 3030757262
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: OMG YES I WAS HOPING YOU WOULD ASK THAT! Have you heard the news
      about...
    characterEmotion: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828018104
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1301.8975, y: 373.46564}
    guid:
      Part1: 2998628211
      Part2: 1161274915
      Part3: 3824780930
      Part4: 2435732279
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: "And what an interesting bunch they are! \nYou see, the boss over
      there at the counter seems to be the least interesting of them, all grumpy
      and stone-faced.\nBetween him and the other guest, who looks like he swats
      flies with a revolver, I can't decide which one looks the most like they would
      kill me..."
    characterEmotion: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828018107
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1421.0004, y: -26.99998}
    guid:
      Part1: 3567248338
      Part2: 1222346820
      Part3: 1553846463
      Part4: 3527411740
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: "Then, there's the help, which concerns me in a different fashion...\nThat
      girl over there, the maid... she seems so nervous, poor thing... I wonder what
      happened to her.\nAnd the chef back there... good lord, he looks like my ex-husband!
      *shivers* \nSorry, I had a very unpleasant memory just now. Anyways, where
      was I..."
    characterEmotion: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828018108
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2917, y: -159}
    guid:
